<small>
<u><a href="https://github.com/Tampa/DirectoryLister">Directory Lister</a></u> is a simple PHP script that lists the contents of any web-accessible directory and
<br>allows navigating there within. Simply upload Directory Lister to any directory and get immediate
<br>access to all files and sub-directories under that directory. Directory Lister is written in PHP and JavaScript.
<br>=======================================================================================
<br><b>Features</b>
<br>-Extremely simple installation, no database, additional servers, just drop the files and configure -
<br>-Creates on-the-fly listing of any web-accessible directory                                        -
<br>-Customizable sort order of files/folders                                                          -
<br>-Easily define hidden files to be excluded from the listing                                        -
<br>-Download of entire directories as zip                                                             -
<br>-Various sorting options                                                                           -
<br>-Directory size information                                                                        -
<br>-File hashing                                                                                      -
<br>-Custom directory descriptions(place .desc file in directory)                                      -
<br>-Download counter                                                                                  -
